title: Cowboys-Patriots, Aaron Rodgers, Russell Wilson, and where Colin was right & wrong
itunes:title: Cowboys-Patriots, Aaron Rodgers, Russell Wilson, and where Colin was right & wrong
description:
Colin talks about the Dallas Cowboys loss to the New England Patriots and how to fix the Cowboys poor play, Aaron Rodgers horrible performance against the San Francisco 49ers, why he thinks Russell Wilson is better than Rodgers, and where he was right and wrong over the weekend. Guests include Michael Vick, Jesse Holley, AJ Hawk, and Trent Dilfer.
